              <p class=" fs-8 text-accent">28px - 32.1% Line Height (Normal) - 0px Letter Spacing</p>
              <p class="m-0 fs-6 ff-serif">384,400 km</p>
          </article>
          <article class="">
              <p class=" fs-8 ">Text Preset 7 - Barlow Condensed Regular</p>
              <p class=" fs-8 text-accent">14px - 16.8% Line Height (Normal) - 2px Letter Spacing</p>
              <p class="m-0 fs-7 ff-sans-cond">AVG. DISTANCE</p>
          </article>
