              <p class=" fs-8 ">Text Preset 8 - Barlow Condensed Regular</p>
              <p class=" fs-8 text-accent">16px - 19.2% Line Height (Normal) - 2px Letter Spacing</p>
              <p class="m-0 fs-8 ff-sans-cond">EUROPA</p>
          </article>
          <article class="">
              <p class=" fs-8 ">Text Preset 9 - Barlow Regular</p>
